distrib/sets/lists/modules/md.amd64		1.42

	Add dtrace modules to amd64-xen module set list.  Hi jnemeth!
	[riastradh, ticket #21]

sys/kern/subr_cprng.c				1.25

	Lock cprng->cs_lock around rndsink_request to avoid race with callback.
